For your example, you&#39;d mock and verify that request like:

```java
// Given
httpClientMock
  .onPost(&quot;http://localhost:1234&quot;)
  .withBody(is(&quot;example&quot;))
  .doReturn(200, &quot;ok&quot;);

// When
/* call your function here */

// Then
httpClientMock
  .verify()
  .post(&quot;http://localhost:1234&quot;)
  .withBody(is(&quot;example&quot;))
  .called(1);
```

